Word Star Academy — third-party data attribution
=================================================

The bundled word packs in lib/wordpacks/generated/ are derived (trimmed +
re-enriched offline) from the following open datasets. Full source datasets are
NOT redistributed in this repo; only small extracted subsets are committed.

ECDICT — https://github.com/skywind3000/ECDICT
  License: MIT
  Used for: graded/exam word selection (tags zk/gk/cet4/cet6/ky/toefl/ielts/gre)
  and phonetic/translation enrichment.

DictionaryData — https://github.com/LinXueyuanStdio/DictionaryData
  License: Apache-2.0
  Used for: textbook-by-unit word lists (人教/外研/译林 … by book + Unit).

Official syllabus (课程标准 附录词汇表), Ministry of Education, China
  Public domain. Used (optionally) as a coverage/alignment whitelist.

See docs/word-resources.md and docs/word-integration-plan.md for details.
